### [Ruth Chapter 2](../../../bib/kjv/rut002.htm#001.md)

[Ruth](../../../bib/kjv/rut001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">rut 2:0</span></span>

Overview

[Rut 2:1](../../../bib/kjv/rut002.htm#001.md), Ruth gleans in the field of
Boaz; [Rut 2:4](../../../bib/kjv/rut002.htm#004.md), Boaz takes notice of
her, [Rut 2:8](../../../bib/kjv/rut002.htm#008.md), and shews her great
favour; [Rut 2:18](../../../bib/kjv/rut002.htm#018.md), That which she got,
she carries to Naomi.

